  attackDescription: "Heavy augmented strikes combined with a built\u2011in electric
    pistol capable of firing charged energy rounds."
  defenseDescription: Reinforced cybernetic plating absorbs incoming damage and reduces
    impact from heavy hits.
  speedDescription: Moderate mobility with short mechanical bursts that allow quick
    repositioning despite his heavy frame.
  ultimateDescription: "Electro Pulse Shot \u2014 a powerful high\u2011voltage projectile
    that pierces defenses and briefly stuns the target."
  story: "Once a top\u2011tier fighter critically injured in a covert operation,
    he was rebuilt using experimental cybernetic technology. The reconstruction enhanced
    his strength, durability, and reflexes, but left him struggling to balance his
    remaining humanity with the cold efficiency of his mechanical body. His built\u2011in
    electric pistol and the devastating Electro Pulse Shot make him a formidable
    force on the battlefield."
  shortDescription: A reinforced cybernetic fighter with strong durability and a
    devastating electric pulse shot.
